#DATABASE: Cordon_Esquel

#Variables:
#SITE: code of sampling site
#YEAR: year of sampling
#LAT: latitude
#LON: longitude
#ALTITUDE: altitude (masl)    
#ELEVATION: position of each wetland across altitudinal gradient (SA: subandean - below treeline, AN: andean - above treeline)
#TEMPERATURE: water temperature (°C)
#CONDUCTIVITY: water conductivity (microSiemens/cm)
#TDS: total dissolved solids (mg/l)   
#OD: dissolved oxygen (mg/l)          
#POR_OD: oxygen saturation (%)
#PH: pH
#TSS: total suspended solids (mg/l)
#PO4: phosphate (microgram/l)
#NH4:ammonium (microgram/l)
#NO3NO2: nitrate + nitrite (microgram/l)
#RICHNESS: richness of macroinvertebrates (number of taxa)     
#ABUNDANCE: abundance of macroinvertebrates (individuals/m3)    
#LCBD: local contribution to beta diversity        

